claudemeter.thresholds.tokens.profiles.markdownDescription:
Per-profile threshold overrides. **Deep-merge semantics**: leaf-field values are merged over the built-in profile; unset fields inherit from the built-in.

Example:
```json
{
  "max-20x": {
    "thresholds": {
      "warningRunwayTokens": 30000
    }
  }
}
```
Above keeps every other `max-20x` field at its built-in default and only overrides the warning-runway value.
